description:
The New Frontier!

We stand on the threshold mof a new era for mankind, for we have begun our march toward a new frontier of knowledge and understanding. The stars, the Moon, the outer planets are surely within our reach!

Preposterous? Ridiculous? NO! Remember the lessons taught us by the past! Yesterday's miracle is today's accepted fact! Today's knowledge and the advances the future will bring, puts nothing beyond the realm of attainment! Men of genius, working in many fields of scientific endeavor, slowly but surely unravel the secrets of the Earth and the cosmos; even of man, of life itself!

Here in this magazine we bring you the essence of mankind's eternal dream...the conquest of space! Scientific material employed in this book is authentic and based upon known scientific fact! Here, in these pages, we open to you a great new phase in the development of mankind so that you can keep pace with the birth of the most exciting and awesome era since the beginning of time on Earth!

Here is the present and the future! Here is mankind, you and I and your neighbors and friends, struggling upward to new heights, toward the glorious, unknown, new frontier...OUTER SPACE!


